<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif">Alguns elementos que podem ser encontrados em guias de Entidades:</span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif">Caboclos: sementes de a&ccedil;a&iacute;, esmeralda, dentes, penas;</span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif">Preto Velho: L&aacute;grimas de Nossa Senhora, cruz, ros&aacute;rio;</span></span></li>
