	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif">Exu: olho de cabra, &ocirc;nix, hematita, obsidiana, tridente, b&uacute;zios pretos, caveira de resina; e</span></span></li>
